{"type":"answer","id":15535,"parentType":"question","parentId":3386,"uid":2356,"contents":"朝鲜还是免费福利分配住房呢。<br>\n<br>\n1950-1990年代初的中国大陆也是单位包福利分配房子，免费的房子。<br>\n<br>\n在这实现居者有其屋这点上，我看胡耀邦，赵紫阳，万里和邓小平等诸公的贡献不容抹杀。<br>\n<br>\nToo young too simple, sometimes naive.<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541074471705206.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541074471705206.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541074471705206.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-11-02","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}